---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use | InterestDecor"
  description="InterestDecor terms of use — the rules and guidelines for using our website and content."
>

<div class="page-hero">
  <p class="page-hero-eyebrow">Legal</p>
  <h1 class="page-hero-title">Terms of <em>Use</em></h1>
  <p class="page-hero-desc">Last updated: June 2026</p>
</div>

<section class="legal-section">
  <div class="container legal-container">

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing and using <strong>interestdecor.com</strong> (the "Site"), you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use this Site.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2>2. Use of Content</h2>
      <p>All content on InterestDecor — including blog posts, photographs, graphics, text, and guides — is the intellectual property of InterestDecor unless otherwise stated.</p>
      <p>You may:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Read, save, and share our content for personal, non-commercial use</li>
        <li>Share links to our content on social media and Pinterest</li>
        <li>Quote brief excerpts with clear attribution and a link back to the original post</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You may not:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Copy, reproduce, or republish our full articles or images without written permission</li>
        <li>Use our content for commercial purposes without consent</li>
        <li>Remove any copyright or attribution notices from our content</li>
        <li>Scrape or automatically extract content from this Site</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2>3. Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>InterestDecor participates in affiliate marketing programmes. Some links on this Site are affiliate links — when you click and make a purchase, we may earn a small commission at no additional cost to you.</p>
      <p>We only recommend products and services we genuinely believe will be useful to our readers. Affiliate relationships never influence our editorial content or opinions.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2>4. Accuracy of Information</h2>
      <p>We make every effort to ensure the information on InterestDecor is accurate, helpful, and up to date. However, we make no warranties or representations about the accuracy, completeness, or suitability of any content for your particular circumstances.</p>
      <p>DIY and craft projects involve inherent risks. Always follow safety guidelines and use appropriate protective equipment. InterestDecor is not responsible for any injury, damage, or loss resulting from following our tutorials or advice.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2>5. External Links</h2>
      <p>InterestDecor may contain links to external websites. These links are provided for convenience and information purposes only. We have no control over the content of external sites and accept no responsibility for them or for any loss or damage that may arise from using them.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2>6. User Comments & Submissions</h2>
      <p>If you submit comments, ideas, or content to InterestDecor (via contact form, email, or social media), you grant us a non-exclusive, royalty-free licence to use, reproduce, and publish that content. We will always credit you where appropriate.</p>
      <p>We reserve the right to remove any content that is offensive, spam, or in violation of these terms.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2>7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p>This Site is provided "as is" without any warranties of any kind, express or implied. We do not warrant that the Site will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses or other harmful components.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, InterestDecor shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of this Site or reliance on any content published here.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2>9. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to update these Terms of Use at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting. Continued use of the Site after changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2>10. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These Terms of Use shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws. Any disputes shall be resolved through good-faith negotiation wherever possible.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2>11. Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about these Terms of Use, please contact us:</p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> rajamashoodelahi@gmail.com</p>
      <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="/contact/">interestdecor.com/contact/</a></p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.legal-section {
  padding: 80px 0 96px;
}

.legal-container {
  max-width: 780px;
}

.legal-block {
  margin-bottom: 48px;
  padding-bottom: 48px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.legal-block:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
  margin-bottom: 0;
  padding-bottom: 0;
}

.legal-block h2 {
  font-family: var(--ff-display);
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--dark);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.legal-block p {
  font-size: .95rem;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.85;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.legal-block ul {
  padding-left: 20px;
  margin: 12px 0;
}

.legal-block li {
  font-size: .95rem;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  list-style: disc;
}

.legal-block a {
  color: var(--rose);
  text-decoration: underline;
  text-underline-offset: 3px;
}

.legal-block a:hover {
  color: var(--dusty);
}
</style>